item.description: There is a permission and access control vulnerability in some ZTE AndroidTV STBs. Due to improper permission settings, non-privileged application can perform functions that are protected with signature/privilege-level permissions. Exploitation of this vulnerability could clear personal data and applications on the user's device, affecting device operation.
